98
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:38,833
You want the upper or lower half?

99
00:10:38,833 --> 00:10:41,292
Do you really think I won't call the police?

100
00:10:42,958 --> 00:10:45,167
Do the cops know where your son is?

101
00:10:47,208 --> 00:10:53,208
