a high-ranking official.

266
00:21:14,375 --> 00:21:16,500
Now the cheaper, the better.

267
00:21:17,833 --> 00:21:20,250
We have a population of 10 million.

268
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,708
Say RMB¥1K a set,

269
00:21:24,625 --> 00:21:27,208
