270
00:21:27,208 --> 00:21:30,833
We will be fatter than Chow Yun-fat!

271
00:21:31,917 --> 00:21:35,708
Beepers are already outdated.

272
00:21:36,958 --> 00:21:41,542
OK, I'll talk to you later.

273
