916
01:05:07,500 --> 01:05:08,750
Big Bro Chiu.

917
01:06:57,333 --> 01:06:58,000
Hey.

918
01:06:58,000 --> 01:07:01,708
Mr Cheuk, you know who Kun-xi is?

919
01:07:02,208 --> 01:07:04,500
It's Kun-xi speaking.

920
01:07:04,500 --> 01:07:08,708
Look me up in Guangdong. I won't let you down.

921
01:07:19,958 --> 01:07:23,333
You're really quitting? It's a cushy job.

922
01:07:23,333 --> 01:07:24,750
You're telling me!

923
