1036
01:17:34,958 --> 01:17:35,667
Hello?

1037
01:17:35,958 --> 01:17:36,792
Hey!

1038
01:17:37,250 --> 01:17:37,875
Hey!

1039
01:17:42,000 --> 01:17:43,083
You are dead!

1040
01:17:43,500 --> 01:17:44,750
Go up!

1041
01:17:44,917 --> 01:17:46,000
Go up!

1042
01:17:48,208 --> 01:17:49,167
Hello?

1043
01:17:49,792 --> 01:17:51,000
Speak!

1044
01:17:51,542 --> 01:17:53,208
Are you Cheuk?

1045
01:17:54,042 --> 01:17:55,000
Who's speaking?

1046
01:18:01,042 --> 01:18:02,500
Kwai Ching-hung.

1047
01:18:04,958 --> 01:18:06,542
Need my help?

1048
01:18:07,958 --> 01:18:09,542
Are you kidding me?

1049
01:18:11,292 --> 01:18:13,333
Do you have any proof?

1050
01:18:14,250 --> 01:18:17,083
I robbed Tung Shing Watch in 1986.

1051
01:18:17,875 --> 01:18:19,375
I killed 3 plainclothes

1052
01:18:19,375 --> 01:18:21,042
in 1988.

1053
01:18:21,333 --> 01:18:22,625
And Landmark in 1992…

1054
01:18:23,875 --> 01:18:27,458
Wasn't it Yip who robbed Landmark in 1992!

1055
01:18:29,875 --> 01:18:31,958
Don't be so gullible.

1056
01:18:32,583 --> 01:18:36,083
Jumbo Watch in 1994
and Lucky Guy Jewellery two years ago.

1057
01:18:36,083 --> 01:18:37,833
I did them all.

1058
01:18:37,833 --> 01:18:39,875
Do you think only Yip had AK-47?

1059
01:18:39,875 --> 01:18:42,583
He loved to be on camera
and the cops were dumb.

1060
01:18:42,583 --> 01:18:45,792
- I just took advantage of the situation…
- Hold on! Don't hang up.

1061
01:18:58,333 --> 01:18:59,667
What did you just say?

1062
01:18:59,667 --> 01:19:00,500
Fuck you!

1063
01:19:00,500 --> 01:19:01,250
Are you playing me?

1064
01:19:03,417 --> 01:19:06,250
It's you, Yip!

1065
01:19:08,458 --> 01:19:11,625
Landmark in 1992, Jumbo in 1994,
and Lucky Guy two years ago.

1066
01:19:11,625 --> 01:19:12,458
Are you responsible for all?

1067
01:19:12,458 --> 01:19:13,500
No!

1068
01:19:13,500 --> 01:19:14,500
I never did my jobs in clandestine!

1069
01:19:14,667 --> 01:19:17,292
Why should I hide myself?

1070
01:19:52,583 --> 01:19:53,542
We're all here.

1071
01:19:53,792 --> 01:19:54,750
Where are you right now?

1072
01:19:54,750 --> 01:19:56,125
Hong Kong!

1073
01:19:57,417 --> 01:19:59,292
I'll call you when I'm back in Hong Kong.

1074
01:20:22,792 --> 01:20:23,792
Hello?

1075
01:20:27,042 --> 01:20:28,042
Hello?

1076
01:20:33,375 --> 01:20:34,542
Hello?

1077
01:20:34,542 --> 01:20:36,625
Kwai Ching-hung, you still there?

1078
01:20:37,292 --> 01:20:37,917
Hello?

1079
01:20:37,917 --> 01:20:38,583
Yes.

1080
01:20:39,417 --> 01:20:40,917
Where are you?

1081
01:20:43,708 --> 01:20:44,625
Hong Kong.

1082
01:20:49,458 --> 01:20:51,417
Call you when I'm back in Hong Kong.

1083
01:20:51,417 --> 01:20:52,625
Let's talk later.

1084
01:21:03,333 --> 01:21:04,875
Motherfucker! The 3 Kings

1085
01:21:04,875 --> 01:21:06,208
of Thieves have nothing to do with you.

1086
01:21:06,875 --> 01:21:08,542
Since you're here,

1087
01:21:09,583 --> 01:21:11,625
