1090
01:21:42,500 --> 01:21:44,375
Mr Cheuk's life

1091
01:21:46,167 --> 01:21:48,583
worth at least $100M!

1092
01:22:00,542 --> 01:22:01,542
Put your guns down!

1093
01:22:04,250 --> 01:22:06,625
Retired soldiers? Go!

1094
01:22:11,917 --> 01:22:13,042
Car key.

1095
01:22:13,750 --> 01:22:15,042
Car key!

1096
01:22:29,583 --> 01:22:31,583
