1097
01:22:33,500 --> 01:22:35,417
If you don't treat me as your Big Bro,
let's split!

1098
01:22:36,250 --> 01:22:38,375
Big Bro, we always follow your orders.

1099
01:22:38,375 --> 01:22:40,500
You said “drop the guns,” we dropped the guns.

1100
01:22:40,500 --> 01:22:41,458
Is that very hard for you?

1101
01:22:41,458 --> 01:22:43,750
No, we always follow you, Big Bro.

1102
01:22:43,750 --> 01:22:45,500
